Package net.mcreator.element.parts

Interface IWorkspaceDependent

All Known Implementing Classes:
AchievementEntry, Animation, AttributeEntry, BiomeEntry, ConfiguredFeatureEntry, DamageTypeEntry, EffectEntry, Enchantment, EntityEntry, Fluid, GameEventEntry, Item.StateEntry, LivingEntity.ModelLayerEntry, MappableElement, MItemBlock, NonMappableElement, Particle, ProfessionEntry, ProjectileEntry, Sound, StepSound, StructureEntry, TabEntry, TextureHolder, UniquelyMappedElement
public interface IWorkspaceDependent
Mod element parameters represented by instances of classes implementing this interface gather some used data from the configured workspace. In other words, these objects need workspace reference defined before they can be used by workspace managers or code generators.
